<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالْعَصْرِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> إِنَّ الْإِنْسَانَ لَفِي خُسْرٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِلَّا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالْحَقِّ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالصَّبْرِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>